093-177b @#/ /yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa bdun la phyag 'tshal lo/ /dgra dang 'jigs pa kun las rgal/ /rnam par gzigs ni gzi brjid che/ /rdzu 'phrul ngo bo gtsug tor te/ /thams cad skyob pa'i shes rab dang / /log dad sel ba'i stobs nyid dang / /gser thub kyi ni bslab pa dang / /'od srung gi ni yon tan dang / /shAkya thub pa'i brtson 'grus kyis/ /bdag ni rtag tu bde bar shog /tad+ya thA/ dza yan+ti/ bi dza yan+ti/ dza ye bi dza yan
